## SPI resolution 2009-10-11.jj.1 (Holding debian.org.tw Domain in trust)

After discussion of the uncertain membership of debian.org.tw and issues
related to transfering SPI assets out of the US, it was decided to defer action
on this resolution until an unambiguous method is determined for SPI to
validate a domain transfer request from debian.org.tw.


